page.title: 09BIOGRAPHY
page.content: A day from my diary. I woke up at 7a.m. and after about 20 minutes I got up,washed,cleaned my teeth ,dressed and went downstairs.I had a boiled egg for breakfast and then I fed Lulu my rabbit. I arrived at school at 8.45 and took my teacher's dog for a walk.After assembly I went to see if I was good enough to run in our area Sports.After play we saw a film "Tooth Care." It told us what to eat and what not to.We were also given a tooth-brush, paste and disclosing tablets. Before lunch we had time for some handwriting prac- tice.After lunch we played "Stuck in the Mud".In the afternoon we had to catch up on Maths and English. At home I had tea,watched television and went to bed at about 8.45.
